3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning to improve image denoising and classification, which are both applications of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with color (multichannel) image denoising, which is a topic related to multimedia. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The proposed method is a neural network architecture, which falls under the sub-field of neural computing.
